title: ‘Unable to answer a question!’: Tucker Carlson clashes with Jehmu Greene
text:
‘Unable to answer a question!’: Tucker Carlson clashes with Jehmu Greene Posted at 10:10 pm on January 16, 2017 by William A. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Jehmu Greene is a Fox News analyst who is running to chair the DNC. Like so many women across the country, I am stepping up and putting myself out there. I am running for DNC Chair. https://t.co/6l3w9AjiGH pic.twitter.com/WhpRnQsaJG 
Greene put herself out there Monday night on “Tucker Carlson Tonight,” where the two debated Rep. John Lewis’s assertion that Donald Trump is not a legitimate president. Tucker Carlson vs Jehmu Greene FULL HEATED Interview https://t.co/BgLVKy9LB6 via @YouTube 
— FILTHY #NEWS (@FILTH
